description=Complete industrial chemistry and biomass processing suite for Project Zomboid Build 42: blackpowder synthesis, biodiesel production, fat rendering, soap-making, bone char, salt extraction, recycling, agriculture, botanical hemp processing, horticulture, water purification, fire starting, leather tanning, construction materials, powered concrete mixer workstation, and advanced lab processes. Features 276 recipes, 101 items, 9 fluids, 19 sandbox options, condition-based purity tracking, tiered reset system, EHR health hazard integration, farming spray integration, Dynamic Trading support with multi-vendor integration, [B42] Horticulture migration, and in-game welcome guide and changelog popups. Requires PhobosLib and Zombie Virus Vaccine.
